[div class=p 
	"Many objects, notably monsters, begin at address 
	[b 
		"7E03C7
	]b
	". Each object is 94 bytes in size. Varik's barrier spell takes the first slot, Varik's projectiles take the next three slots, then Varik himself takes the slot after that. Monsters take up the following 31 slots. There is room for monster projectiles, but this hasn't been measured at this time.
	$LF
]div
